<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也只是徒有其名罢了</font>

258
00:16:05,098 --> 00:16:06,068
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">徒有其名…</font>

259
00:16:07,448 --> 00:16:09,498
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也不用在意婚约的事</font>

260
00:16:09,948 --> 00:16:12,158
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我现在也只是暂代王位</font>

261
00:16:12,788 --> 00:16:15,548
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">几年后我就会退位的</font>

262
00:16:16,628 --> 00:16:19,828
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">相马不想我当你的未婚妻吗</font>

263
00:16:22,238 --> 00:16:24,368
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这么问也太犯规了</font>

264
00:16:24,478 --> 00:16:25,968
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗…</font>

265
00:16:26,988 --> 00:16:31,828
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那莉希雅愿意我当你的未婚夫吗</font>

266
00:16:32,468 --> 00:16:33,318
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我不介意</font>

267
00:16:37,948 --> 00:16:41,798
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟我觉得相马比我更适合当国王</font>

268
00:16:42,098 --> 00:16:44,248
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为我更适合当国王才愿意的吗…</font>

269
00:16:45,238 --> 00:16:47,578
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你要和不喜欢的对象订婚吗</font>

270
00:16:49,308 --> 00:16:50,858
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">王室就是这样的</font>

271
00:16:51,838 --> 00:16:53,488
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我又不是王室成员</font>

272
00:16:53,928 --> 00:16:54,578
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且</font>

273
00:16:55,848 --> 00:16:57,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还是喜欢自由恋爱的婚姻</font>

274
00:16:59,468 --> 00:17:05,518
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那相马你讨厌我吗？你能确定我们将来不会相爱吗</font>

275
00:17:16,788 --> 00:17:17,908
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请问…</font>

276
00:17:19,948 --> 00:17:23,538
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还需要装睡多久才好</font>

277
00:17:30,688 --> 00:17:32,708
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么样 很不错吧</font>

278
00:17:32,928 --> 00:17:36,668
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是你用「鲜活的骚灵」操控的对吧</font>

279
00:17:39,078 --> 00:17:41,818
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大概是因为经常使用 所以升级了</font>

280
00:17:42,318 --> 00:17:45,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在我能分出四个独立意识操控物体了</font>

281
00:17:45,908 --> 00:17:49,228
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那也不用把能力用在这种东西上啊</font>

282
00:17:49,918 --> 00:17:50,508
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下</font>

283
00:17:51,908 --> 00:17:54,318
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">马古那家族的家主古雷布·马古那大人</font>

284
00:17:54,578 --> 00:17:56,228
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">带着他的儿子哈尔帕德</font>

285
00:17:56,378 --> 00:18:01,718
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和禁军魔导士枫·狐基西亚求见陛下</font>

286
00:18:03,628 --> 00:18:05,498
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">诸位抬起头来吧</font>

287
00:18:13,438 --> 00:18:17,378
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哈尔帕德 现在的你帅气多了呢</font>

288
00:18:19,638 --> 00:18:24,728
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">恳请陛下宽恕犬子的愚行</font>

289
00:18:26,538 --> 00:18:28,378
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">愚行是指昨天的事情吗</font>

290
00:18:29,228 --> 00:18:32,078
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">枫已经将详细情况告知臣</font>

291
00:18:32,868 --> 00:18:35,108
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">犬子对陛下的恶语中伤</font>

292
00:18:35,418 --> 00:18:39,768
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">甚至妄图投靠三公爵的荒谬言论 简直可恶至极</font>

293
00:18:40,728 --> 00:18:43,178
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下发怒也是理所应当</font>

294
00:18:43,278 --> 00:18:48,828
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这全出于臣教子无方 还请降罪于臣一人</font>

295
00:18:49,888 --> 00:18:54,538
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">照这个逻辑 让臣子说出这种话 也是我领导无方了</font>

296
00:18:55,128 --> 00:18:56,278
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我没打算追究</font>

297
00:18:56,988 --> 00:18:57,788
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下！</font>

298
00:18:58,578 --> 00:19:03,088
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">更何况 他看上去已经受到足够的惩罚了</font>

299
00:19:03,748 --> 00:19:06,508
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感谢陛下宽宏大量</font>

300
00:19:07,398 --> 00:19:13,268
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">待臣回到家中 定然用这双手好好锤炼犬子</font>

301
00:19:15,288 --> 00:19:17,008
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你注意分寸</font>

302
00:19:17,758 --> 00:19:24,108
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且要是再让他那张脸受伤…往奇怪的方向发展</font>

303
00:19:24,108 --> 00:19:25,708
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">枫就要伤心了吧</font>

304
00:19:30,158 --> 00:19:34,488
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对了 本来打算近期说的 但这次时机正好</font>

305
00:19:34,868 --> 00:19:36,318
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我现在就宣布吧</font>

306
00:19:38,918 --> 00:19:42,098
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">禁军魔导士枫·狐基西亚</font>

307
00:19:42,538 --> 00:19:42,998
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">臣在</font>

308
00:19:44,088 --> 00:19:47,608
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">以阁下之才身居魔导士一职实在浪费</font>

309
00:19:48,258 --> 00:19:52,338
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我命你加入近卫骑士团卢德文团长麾下 担任参谋一职</font>

310
00:19:53,068 --> 00:19:53,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是</font>

311
00:19:54,418 --> 00:19:56,768
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么？让我当参谋？</font>

312
00:19:57,268 --> 00:19:59,898
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">最重要的是人才的质量与物资</font>

313
00:20:00,698 --> 00:20:02,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">昨天你在「罗蕾莱」是这么说的吧</font>

314
00:20:06,728 --> 00:20:08,468
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你和我在思想上应该很合拍</font>

315
00:20:09,818 --> 00:20:11,348
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">属下惶恐</font>

316
00:20:12,968 --> 00:20:17,288
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后是哈尔帕德·马古那 我命你从陆军转至禁军</font>

317
00:20:18,148 --> 00:20:19,788
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">把我分配到禁军？</font>

318
00:20:20,528 --> 00:20:23,178
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 今后你作为枫的副官</font>

319
00:20:23,728 --> 00:20:27,168
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在她身边辅佐她 听到了吗</font>

320
00:20:29,068 --> 00:20:29,628
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是</font>

321
00:20:32,598 --> 00:20:35,168
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好了 那今天就先…</font>

322
00:20:35,458 --> 00:20:41,468
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下 非常抱歉 还需要占据您一点时间</font>

323
00:20:41,988 --> 00:20:44,538
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">臣有事想要上报陛下</font>

324
00:20:45,518 --> 00:20:47,288
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么事 你说吧</font>

325
00:20:48,228 --> 00:20:53,768
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个…这件事不便在大庭广众之下谈论</font>

326
00:20:54,428 --> 00:20:55,648
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请陛下屏退左右</font>

327
00:21:04,948 --> 00:21:06,768
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好了 你要说什么</font>

328
00:21:07,928 --> 00:21:08,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是</font>

329
00:21:13,968 --> 00:21:18,158
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">非常感谢公主邀请我们来喝茶</font>

330
00:21:18,458 --> 00:21:22,778
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">古雷布大人报告的这段时间 待着也无趣</font>

331
00:21:23,088 --> 00:21:24,778
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们就在这里喝喝茶聊聊天吧</font>

332
00:21:25,278 --> 00:21:26,508
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这真是个好主意</font>

333
00:21:26,688 --> 00:21:30,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难得有机会 不如聊一聊关系亲密的男女</font>

334
00:21:30,718 --> 00:21:34,458
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">平时是如何增进感情的吧</font>

335
00:21:36,348 --> 00:21:39,378
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对公主殿下一定会有所帮助的</font>

336
00:21:39,688 --> 00:21:40,618
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">瑟林娜！</font>

337
00:21:41,078 --> 00:21:43,138
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那请允许我等僭越…</font>

338
00:21:43,138 --> 00:21:44,778
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你们不要这么认真啊</font>

339
00:21:49,538 --> 00:21:54,418
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这么说 是想让我做什么呢</font>

340
00:21:55,048 --> 00:21:55,968
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">并没有</font>

341
00:21:57,308 --> 00:22:01,338
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">臣只是觉得 陛下有必要知道这件事</font>

342
00:22:03,978 --> 00:22:05,048
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">太沉重了…</font>

343
00:22:09,988 --> 00:22:13,938
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风 穿越整个世界</font>

344
00:22:14,168 --> 00:22:18,288
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连接不可能相遇的我们</font>

345
00:22:18,388 --> 00:22:22,418
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">展开没有人看得见的羽翼</font>

346
00:22:22,598 --> 00:22:26,528
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找寻没有人看得见的奇迹</font>

347
00:22:26,528 --> 00:22:29,838
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">起飞吧</font>

348
00:22:35,428 --> 00:22:39,568
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">继续迷惘明日的方向</font>

349
00:22:39,618 --> 00:22:43,718
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">追求继续选择的勇气</font>

350
00:22:43,858 --> 00:22:47,928
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不曾怀疑天空有多蓝</font>

351
00:22:47,988 --> 00:22:52,388
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我能毫不畏惧世事无常</font>

352
00:22:52,588 --> 00:22:54,808
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起将来的梦想</font>

353
00:22:54,808 --> 00:22:56,898
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">超越想象中的未来</font>

354
00:22:56,898 --> 00:23:00,958
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这般时光是如此美好</font>

355
00:23:01,198 --> 00:23:03,258
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只想徜徉在其中</font>

356
00:23:03,378 --> 00:23:05,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你共同度过现在</font>

357
00:23:05,428 --> 00:23:08,798
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是能实现就好了</font>

358
00:23:08,798 --> 00:23:13,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">穿过湛蓝 绵延不断的天空</font>

359
00:23:13,738 --> 00:23:17,428
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将轮回的命运拉近身边</font>

360
00:23:17,428 --> 00:23:21,848
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">传达思念给紧握的手</font>

361
00:23:21,848 --> 00:23:26,588
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅仅希望这就是永远</font>

362
00:23:26,648 --> 00:23:28,638
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使现在只是幻影</font>

363
00:23:28,838 --> 00:23:31,028
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算是在某人的梦境里</font>

364
00:23:31,028 --> 00:23:32,758
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风</font>

365
00:23:32,758 --> 00:23:37,598
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在抓住它 起飞吧</font>

